node.text:
Having grown up in Quebec, I can only imagine how hard this last year must have been for maple syrup producers, which is why I was thrilled to hear that @netflixca is supporting this beloved industry with a $10,000 donation to @macabanemaison. What’s your favourite way to enjoy maple syrup? 

Ayant grandi au Québec, je ne peux qu’imaginer à quel point la dernière année a dû être difficile pour les propriétaires de cabanes à sucre. C’est pourquoi je suis si enthousiaste de savoir que @netflixca va soutenir cette industrie que nous aimons tant en faisant un don de 10 000 $ à l'initiative @macabanemaison. Et vous, quelle place faites-vous au sirop d’érable dans votre vie?

node.text: Karen and Winnie from @quaraneat teach me how to make classic scallion pancakes with “trifecta” sauce. We also shed light on www.stopaapihate.org which offers resources on how to report anti-Asian hate incidents as well as their advocacy for local, state and national policies reinforcing human and civil rights protections. @winwinli13 @kliiiii808 @stopaapihate

node.text:
For @glsen's 30th anniversary, I'm honored to present Darid's incredible story and celebrate their leadership and activism to improve the lives of LGBTQ+ students. 

Through these stories, GLSEN showcases how we can create #RespectEverywhere and allow LGBTQ+ students to flourish across the country. 

Join me in supporting GLSEN today by making a donation for their fight to ensure that schools, families, and peers respect and support LGBTQ+ students everywhere - link in bio

node.text: Throwback to my Austin kitchen and the city that made this NY heat wave feel like a brisk fall day. TX brought me a lot of skills - paddle boarding, the ability to spot snakes underwater that were actually just sticks, but most importantly, snacking through the heat. It’s there that I got hooked on these refrigerated protein balls 🤤 featuring @ollynutrition collagen peptides. If you didn't know, my favorite gummy vitamin company also makes their own line of collagen. I love adding this flavor-less powder to my smoothies, coffee, and, yes, even these protein balls. Adding collagen to your diet is a great way to increase a natural occurring supplement that supports strong nails, hair, and bones 🦴 (helpful for my many, many paddle board falls) and Olly has 10 grams of it! #ollysponsored #proteinballs #hotasballs

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Antoni Porowski in Blackberry Farm with @blackberryfarm, and @neonthemutt. May be an image of 2 people and people standing.

node.text: Today I met John Coykendall, artist and @blackberryfarm master gardener. I don’t think I’ve ever interacted with a person who embodies a sense of purpose stronger than John. We talked about potatoes, our mutual love of Eastern European soups and the importance of documenting history, be it recipes, beans or where we come from. I left with the reminder that we all have a reason to be here and our goal is to figure out what that is. Every life is worth living. I left with a large bunch of mint from his garden and when I got to my room I made mint tea with sugar like my parents did when I was a kid on hot Montreal summer nights after dinner (mint my father smuggled from Morocco, of course.)
